Modifications
-------------

This fork is maintained by Diego Petrucci as part of The Last Harness
(https://github.com/diegopetrucci/the-last-harness). It is trimmed to:

  - Exa search only (Perplexity, Gemini API/Web, browser-cookie auth,
    video, PDF, GitHub clone cache, curator UI, and the bundled
    librarian skill are removed).
  - The three tools web_search, fetch_content, get_search_content.
  - Isolated configuration under $PI_CODING_AGENT_DIR (no ~/.pi access).
  - Code-side request safety (scheme allowlist, DNS-rebinding-resistant
    host-deny list, per-task fetch budget, per-response size cap).

Full spec: docs/web-search-spec.md in the parent harness repo.

See CHANGELOG.md for the per-release list of changes.
